                                                Once again, welcome to [Company Name]. We are confident that you will find your time here both rewarding and fulfilling. If you need anything at all, please do not hesitate to ask. We believe in open communication and are always here to help.
                                            </td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;">
                                            <td class="content-block" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif; color: #878a99; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: top; margin: 0; padding: 0 0 10px;" valign="top">
                                                Hereâ€™s to a successful and enjoyable journey with us!
                                            </td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;">
                                            <td class="content-block" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif; color: #878a99; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: top; margin: 0; padding: 0 0 10px;" valign="top">
                                                <span style="font-weight: 800;">Designation:</span> 
                                            </td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;">
                                            <td class="content-block" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif; color: #878a99; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: top; margin: 0; padding: 0 0 10px;" valign="top">
                                                <span style="font-weight: 800;">Email:</span> 
                                            </td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;">
                                            <td class="content-block" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif; color: #878a99; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: top; margin: 0; padding: 0 0 10px;" valign="top">
                                                <span style="font-weight: 800;">Password:</span> 
                                            </td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;">
